OL,3,CBee Network to freeze fares and start
OL,4,Call-day concession passes
OL,6,FPlans have been announced to freeze
OL,7,Ffares and lift peak time concession
OL,8,Frestrictions on Greater Manchester's
OL,9,FBee Network.
OL,11,FMayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,12,FBurnham has described the plans as
OL,13,F"the right thing to do". All bus and
OL,14,Ftram fares will be frozen until the
OL,15,Fend of 2026, keeping #2 single bus
OL,16,Ffares for the fourth consecutive year.
