OL,3,CBee Network to freeze fares and start
OL,4,Call-day concession passes
OL,6,FThe 09.30am restriction for
OL,7,Fconcessionary pass holders will be
OL,8,Fremoved, benefitting older and
OL,9,Fdisabled people, after successful
OL,10,Fpilots earlier this year.
OL,12,FMr Burnham and council leaders have
OL,13,Fbeen working with older and disabled
OL,14,Fgroups to bring about the change which
OL,15,Fwill be implemented from 1 March 2026,
OL,16,Fsubject to the confirmation of budgets
OL,17,Fin February 2026.
OL,19,FCurrently, concessionary passes can
OL,20,Fonly be used after 09.30am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
