OL,3,CBee Network to freeze fares and start
OL,4,Call-day concession passes
OL,6,F"The 09.30am restriction is unfair, if
OL,7,Fnot discriminatory.
OL,9,F"People's lives don't start at
OL,10,F09.30am. Older people need to get to
OL,11,Fhealth appointments, look after the
OL,12,Fgrandkids. Disabled people need to get
OL,13,Fout to work.
OL,15,F"The case to remove it was building.
OL,17,FHe added: "It's really unbelievable
OL,18,Fhow much of a difference this makes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
