OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1766882744
OL,3,CBee Network to freeze fares and start
OL,4,Call-day concession passes
OL,6,F"In making this move we will lift the
OL,7,Flives of hundreds of thousands of
OL,8,Fpeople across Greater Manchester.
OL,9,FThey'll just have one less thing to
OL,10,Fworry about as they go into the New
OL,11,FYear.
OL,13,F"This is the right thing to do,
OL,14,Fbecause truthfully, this rule is
OL,15,Fdiscriminatory."
OL,17,FBurnham added: "We're looking at
OL,18,Feverything to remove the worries that
OL,19,Fpeople have got.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
