OL,3,CBee Network to freeze fares and start
OL,4,Call-day concession passes
OL,6,F"It's created a massive uplift of
OL,7,Fpeople using the buses.
OL,9,F"We know people are still struggling
OL,10,Fwith the way things are, and I just
OL,11,Fthought this would help them so they
OL,12,Fcan go into the break with one less
OL,13,Fthing to worry about."
OL,15,FJoy Watson, a local dementia awareness
OL,16,Fcampaigner, said: "I will now be able
OL,17,Fto attend my early morning
OL,18,Fappointments and meet my caregiver at
OL,19,Fa time that is helpful to us both.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
